data.description: Welcome to Glen Eagle Golf & Country Club! This COMPLETELY FURNISHED MOVE IN READY single family home is situated by the 14th Green with views of the manciured golf course. The home features an open floor plan with volume ceilings, tile floors throughout, newer A/C, newer hot water heater, partial impact windows. The kitchen featuring a breakfast nook is finished with white cabinets complimented by quartz counters. Enjoy the low-fee social membership which includes golf May-October, pool, fitness center, tennis, pickleball, bocce ball, cards, planned activities, as well as the Divot restaurant and main clubhouse with full-service dining. Low HOA fee includes cable, internet, landscaping, irrigation, guard gated entrance. Naples vibrant attractions, 5th Avenue shops, dining and beaches are just a short ride away.
